'''四氯化二硼'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，[[化学式|化学式]] B<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>4</sub>。 它是一种无色液体。<ref name=AICR>{{cite book|work=Advances in Inorganic Chemistry and Radiochemistry|title=Low Temperature Condensation|author=P. L. Timms|page=143|date=1972|isbn=0-12-023614-1|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VupzlLU9NB0C&pg=PA143&lpg=PA143#v=onepage&q&f=false}}</ref>

==制备==
现代合成四氯化二硼涉及使用铜对[[三氯化硼|三氯化硼]]进行脱氯。 <ref>{{cite book|doi=10.1002/9780470132500.ch14|chapter=Tetrachlorodiborane(4) (Diboron Tetrachloride)|series=Inorganic Syntheses|pages=74–78|year=1979|volume=19|last1=Timms|first1=Peter L.|title=Inorganic Syntheses|isbn=9780470132500}}</ref>
它也可以在低温下通过三氯化硼的[[放电|放电]]形成。 <ref name=AICR/> [[三氯化硼|三氯化硼]]的[[放电|放电]]程序可分为三个步骤： <ref name=Urry2 />
:BCl<sub>3</sub> → BCl<sub>2</sub> + Cl
:Cl + Hg ([[电极|电极]]) → HgCl 或 HgCl<sub>2</sub>
:2 BCl<sub>2</sub> → B<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>4</sub>

==反应==
四氯化二硼可用作[[有机硼化合物|有机硼化合物]]的合成[[试剂|试剂]]。例如，四氯化二硼与[[乙烯|乙烯]]反应：<ref name=Urry1>{{cite journal|last1=Urry|first1=Grant|last2=Kerrigan|first2=James|last3=Parsons|first3=Theran D.|last4=Schlesinger|first4=H. I.|title=Diboron Tetrachloride, B<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>4</sub>, as a Reagent for the Synthesis of Organo-boron Compounds. I. The Reaction of Diboron Tetrachloride with Ethylene|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=76|issue=21|year=1954|pages=5299–5301|issn=0002-7863|doi=10.1021/ja01650a011}}</ref>
:CH<sub>2</sub>=CH<sub>2</sub> + B<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>4</sub> → Cl<sub>2</sub>B–CH<sub>2</sub>–CH<sub>2</sub>–BCl<sub>2</sub>

这个化合物在[[室温|室温]]下极易吸收[[氢气|氢气]]：<ref name=Urry2>{{cite journal|last1=Urry|first1=Grant|last2=Wartik|first2=Thomas|last3=Moore|first3=R. E.|last4=Schlesinger|first4=H. I.|title=The Preparation and Some of the Properties of Diboron Tetrachloride, B<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>4</sub>|journal=Journal of the American Chemical Society|volume=76|issue=21|year=1954|pages=5293–5298|issn=0002-7863|doi=10.1021/ja01650a010}}</ref>

:3 B<sub>2</sub>Cl<sub>4</sub> + 3 H<sub>2</sub> → B<sub>2</sub>H<sub>6</sub> + 4 BCl<sub>3</sub>

